Question 16: How to Show this result based on the given details:

True-answers=6
Wrong -answers=0
Total-questions=6

 

q08-2.png

 

Hint 1:- Use imageview and textview, containers for showing the image and text.

Hint 2:- Add the logic for showing the result based on true, and false values out of total questions.

SOURCE CODE:
String getResultMessage(int trueAnswers, int totalQuestions) {
  if (trueAnswers == totalQuestions) {
    return "Perfect Score! ðŸŽ‰";
  } else if (trueAnswers >= totalQuestions / 2) {
    return "Good Job!";
  } else {
    return "Better Luck Next Time!";
  }
}

String getResultImage(int trueAnswers, int totalQuestions) {
  if (trueAnswers == totalQuestions) {
    return 'assets/success.png'; // full marks
  } else if (trueAnswers >= totalQuestions / 2) {
    return 'assets/okay.png'; // average score
  } else {
    return 'assets/fail.png'; // low score
  }
}


